Step Berikutnya
1. Request Logger Middleware

Karena sekarang belum ada visibility request.

Minimal harus log:

method
URI
status code
latency
IP

Contoh output:

POST /api/v1/orders 201 12ms

Tanpa logger nanti debugging susah.

2. Graceful Shutdown

Sekarang service mati langsung saat CTRL+C.

Production seharusnya:

wait inflight request
close app gracefully
timeout shutdown
3. Get Order By ID

Endpoint penting:

GET /api/v1/orders/:id

Sekarang baru:

create
list
4. Update Status Endpoint

Ini penting buat nanti Kafka flow:

PATCH /api/v1/orders/:id/status

Karena nanti:

payment-service publish paid event
order-service update status
5. Pagination

Sekarang:

SELECT * FROM orders

Tidak scalable.

Harus:

limit
page
total count

swsagger